# NCX TTS Reporter — flat box mesh + collider
# Sized to match the UI panel footprint (approx 540x680 UI units)
# Dimensions: 6.0 (X) x 0.1 (Y) x 7.5 (Z), centered at origin
# Top surface at y=+0.05, bottom at y=-0.05

v  3.0  0.05  3.75
v  3.0  0.05 -3.75
v -3.0  0.05 -3.75
v -3.0  0.05  3.75
v  3.0 -0.05  3.75
v  3.0 -0.05 -3.75
v -3.0 -0.05 -3.75
v -3.0 -0.05  3.75

# Top face (+Y)
f 1 2 3
f 1 3 4

# Bottom face (-Y)
f 5 8 7
f 5 7 6

# +X side
f 1 5 6
f 1 6 2

# -X side
f 4 3 7
f 4 7 8

# +Z side
f 1 4 8
f 1 8 5

